        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"166970\">\n<blockquote>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"166970\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Nice.  Never had a 72 CDP.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>It\u2019s actually a very fine but for whatever reason not at all talked about vintage for the reason. The 1972 Clos des Papes is the best Clos de Papes I ever drank. Four down, one to go, and each bottle just irresistible.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I liked 67. Never see 72 stateside.</p>",
